languages.text:
"Of the baleful pack worthy
was the hunt,
Their name will thunder
at the feast of victory;
Doom's scream I ripped out,
Leaving it to cry
a tongueless, silent wail;
Wolf's howl has flown,
Above hall arches soaring..."
{n}Ulfar falls silent and gives you a pensive look.{/n}

